# npm registry 配置
registry=https://registry.npmmirror.com

# Electron / electron-builder 二进制镜像（国内必开，否则 postinstall 会从 GitHub 拉几十~百 MB，极慢像「卡住」）
# npm 10+ 可能对这两行提示 Unknown project config：多数情况下仍会注入 npm_config_* 给子进程，可忽略警告。
# 若将来某版 npm 彻底不生效，请在安装前设置环境变量：
#   ELECTRON_MIRROR、ELECTRON_BUILDER_BINARIES_MIRROR（见 npmmirror 文档）
electron_mirror=https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/electron/
electron_builder_binaries_mirror=https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/electron-builder-binaries/
